---

- **/* read (Can read all files in the workspace)

# Preferred Tools
*Tools that are preferred for this mode*

- Ask the user (Primary tool for gathering information)
- read_file (For understanding context before asking)
- codebase_search (For finding relevant context)
- list_dir (For understanding project structure)
- run_terminal_cmd (For gathering system information)
- Web search (For researching context and forming better questions)
- Documentation consultation:
  - User-added documentation (For understanding existing knowledge)
  - Cursor rules (For understanding requirements)
  - Templates (For understanding standards)
- Git tools:
  - Git history (For understanding past decisions)
  - Git blame (For knowing who to ask)
  - Git log (For understanding project evolution)
